Title: Take My Life, Please!
Plot: A legendary comic from the good old days of Las Vegas is set to reunite with his partner on stage for one night only, until one half of the famous duo is found dead.
GuestStars: Jorja Fox, John Barbour, Marcus Coloma, Kayla Ewell, Shaun Sipos, Eric Ladin, Samantha Shelton, Hedy Burress, Gerald McCullough, Larry Sullivan, Jennifer Tilly, Tim Conway
